## SessionResolutionSummary interface

Summary of the workflow's attempts to resolve the outcome a failed countersigning session. This tracks the numbers of attempts and the outcome of the most recent attempt.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export interface SessionResolutionSummary 
```

[attempts](./client.sessionresolutionsummary.attempts.md)


</td><td>


</td><td>

number


</td><td>

How many attempts have been made to resolve the session.

Attempts are made according to the frequency specified by \[RETRY\_UNKNOWN\_SESSION\_STATE\_DELAY\].

This count is only correct for the current run of the Holochain conductor. If the conductor is restarted then this counter is also reset.


</td></tr>
